Text: RE AnnouncmentSuggested changes to the announcement ONEOK WesTex can only offer interruptible transportation to and from the TW interconnect I am not suggesting this be included in the announcement but I wanted to clarify with you the contractual arrangement ONEOK can offer shippers on our pipeline to and from the interconnect Please include in your announcement the following contact names for ONEOK Butch Cheatham for gas transportation on ONEOK WesTex and Hayley Nealis for gas storage opportunities on the ONEOK WesTex system Original Message From Hyatt Kevin mailtoKevin NRONcom Sent Tuesday August AM To Subject Announcment Importance High Oneok Announcementdoc Butch please review and let me know if this is OK today thanks Kevin This email is the property of Enron Corp andor its relevant affiliate and may contain confidential and privileged material for the sole use of the intended recipient s Any review use distribution or disclosure by others is strictly prohibited If you are not the intended recipient or authorized to receive for the recipient please contact the sender or reply to Enron Corp at and delete all copies of the message This email and any attachments hereto are not intended to be an offer or an acceptance and do not create or evidence a binding and enforceable contract between Enron Corp or any of its affiliates and the intended recipient or any other party and may not be relied on by anyone as the basis of a contract by estoppel or otherwise Thank you
